<p>Book of John <a href="https://content.wtsbooks.com/shopify/pdf_links/9781433558955f.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">https://content.wtsbooks.com/shopify/pdf_links/9781433558955f.pdf</a></p>



<p>There is help out there. If you see someone who looks like she needs help, take time to get to know that person. Ask questions.<br>If you could go anywhere in the world, where would you go?<br>What’s you’re favorite sport, color, food…<br>What are your plans for upcoming holiday/weekend?</p>



<p>Finally, be a friend. Find someone who seems isolated.  Offer her a Pop-tart a smile and some encouragement.  Find out what kind of music he or she likes. Just start talking. Just show that you care. And smile. Keep your smile, it still works and it looks good on you.</p>
